### Player Endpoints

### Get all players
GET http://localhost:7070/fantasyfootball/api/players
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a specific player
GET http://localhost:7070/fantasyfootball/api/players/3
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new player (Requires ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:7070/fantasyfootball/api/players
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "Cristiano Ronaldo",
  "position": "Forward",
  "teamId": 1,
  "performanceRating": 9
}

###

### Update a player (Requires ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:7070/fantasyfootball/api/players/3
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "Updated Player Name",
  "position": "Midfielder",
  "performanceRating": 8.7,
  "teamId": 2
}

###

### Delete a player (Requires ADMIN)
DELETE http://localhost:7070/fantasyfootball/api/players/4
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
